    "SUMMARY": "Jessy Moulin (born 13 January 1986) is a French professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Ligue 1 club Troyes.\nMoulin played for Saint-Étienne until 2021. He joined the club's reserve team in 2005, joining the first team in 2007 and being sent on loan spells to Arles, Fréjus Saint-Raphaël, and Clermont in the process. He joined Troyes in 2021."
